The argument parser
### ######## ######

The specification I wish to implement:

* The command can take any number of Arguments
    * Command Arguments not Option Arguments
* Options may be indicated by -, / or either
* Parameters may or may not be case sensitive
* Options can have arguments
    * Separated by whitespace
    * Separated by a character: :, =
    * Mandatory Arguments
    * Optional Arguments
* Single Character Options can be combined
* Help text can be displayed by:
    * ?
    * -?
    * -h
    * /?
    * /h
    * -help
    * --help
* -- Escapes all remaining output
